t:', compliance_pct)\n", "intent": "Compute Wollaston Beach yearly counts and average violation rate from 2019-2023 and return compliance percentage rounded to nearest integer."}) [toolUseId=call_oHqqsI2tUzmbpxx5uFM2UMzd]
